org.ietf.nea.pa.serialize.writer.bytebuffer

Class PaAttributeErrorValueWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.serialize.writer.bytebuffer.PaAttributeErrorValueWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImWriter<PaAttributeValueError>, Writer<PaAttributeValueError,ByteBuffer>

     class PaAttributeErrorValueWriter
extends Object
implements ImWriter<PaAttributeValueError>
    Writer to serialize an integrity measurement error attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
